---
title: Louisiana-Style Tilapia with Potato Wedges, Red Cabbage Slaw & Spicy Remoulade
description: Cue the brass band, because your taste buds are about to take a trip to the Big Easy! We’re talking ultra-crunchy, spiced tilapia fillets with sides of cabbage-carrot slaw and crispy potato wedges. It’s all finished with a drizzle of one of our all-time favorite condiments: zingy, creamy remoulade. Now if only this came with beignets for dessert...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/620c1ee55db7411a8f13491e-63a699f5.jpg
